sequenceDiagram
    actor Manager
    participant UI as YogiTrack UI
    participant API as Express API
    participant DB as MongoDB

    Manager->>UI: Click "Add Customer"
    UI->>Manager: Show customer form (first name, last name)
    Manager->>UI: Enter first name + last name
    UI->>API: POST /api/customers/check-name
    API->>DB: Query customers by name (case-insensitive)
    DB-->>API: Match results
    alt Name already exists
        API-->>UI: { exists: true, count: N, matches: [...] }
        UI->>Manager: Show warning with existing customer IDs
        Manager->>UI: Confirm to continue (or cancel)
    else Name is unique
        API-->>UI: { exists: false }
    end
    Manager->>UI: Enter remaining data (address, phone, email, preferred comm.)
    Manager->>UI: Click "Add Customer"
    UI->>UI: Validate required fields
    alt Validation fails
        UI->>Manager: Show field-level error messages
    else Validation passes
        UI->>API: POST /api/customers
        API->>DB: Insert new customer (classBalance = 0)
        DB-->>API: Saved customer with generated customerId (C00001)
        API-->>UI: { customer, confirmationMessage }
        UI->>Manager: Show success + confirmationMessage
    end
